    slug: "why-every-saas-tool-is-adding-ai-features-2026",
    title: "Why Every SaaS Tool Is Adding AI Features in 2026 (And What It Means for Your Stack)",
    date: "Mar 18, 2026",
    excerpt: "AI features are flooding every SaaS category. Here's how to tell what's genuinely useful from what's just marketing noise.",
